<a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot.jpg"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='670'%20height='893'%20viewBox=%270%200%20670%20893%27%3E%3C/svg%3E" loading="lazy" data-lazy="1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right,#95adad 25%,#859f9e 25% 50%,#9cb4b6 50% 75%,#9fa9ab 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#47605a 25%,#625d4a 25% 50%,#87806d 50% 75%,#5a5a5c 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#f4c2a1 25%,#37290f 25% 50%,#56522f 50% 75%,#475150 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#330a08 25%,#fdeadc 25% 50%,#303934 50% 75%,#445050 75%)" decoding="async" data-tf-src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-670x893.jpg" alt="Scorpionfish on Dropshot" width="670" height="893" class="tf_svg_lazy alignnone size-large wp-image-22281" data-tf-srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-670x893.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-225x300.jpg 225w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-190x253.jpg 190w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot.jpg 1050w" data-tf-sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /><noscript><img decoding="async" data-tf-not-load src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-670x893.jpg" alt="Scorpionfish on Dropshot" width="670" height="893" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-22281" srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-670x893.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-225x300.jpg 225w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-190x253.jpg 190w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scorpionfish-dropshot.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /></noscript></a><br />
Feels like the scorpionfish really got going on the central south coast this past couple of weeks. Nice to find a few. And to spend a bit of time with the Megabass Shoreluck Ja-Ko softbait. </p></div></div></div></article> <article id="post-22238" class="post tf_clearfix cat-7 post-22238 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-notes tag-hardbaits tag-jdm tag-jigheads tag-metal-jig tag-prime-angling tag-squid-jigs tag-viewing-tanks has-post-title has-post-date has-post-category has-post-tag has-post-comment has-post-author "><div class="post-inner tf_clearfix"><span class="post-icon"></span><time datetime="2025-05-30" class="post-date entry-date updated">30th May, 2025</time><h2 class="post-title entry-title"><a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/2025/05/latest-jdm-tackle-at-prime-angling/">Latest JDM Tackle at Prime Angling</a></h2><div class="post-content"> <div class="entry-content"> <p><a href="https://primeangling.co.uk/collections/jdm-lure-fishing/?sca_ref=3894212.AYJkJGQRZd&#038;sca_source=post-300525"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='670'%20height='299'%20viewBox=%270%200%20670%20299%27%3E%3C/svg%3E" loading="lazy" data-lazy="1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right,#dbaca2 25%,#fbeff1 25% 50%,#d2dbda 50% 75%,#363636 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#fefffd 25%,#c3ada2 25% 50%,#fffefd 50% 75%,#ffffff 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#fefefe 25%,#ffffff 25% 50%,#fdfdfd 50% 75%,#ffffff 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#fefdff 25%,#ffffff 25% 50%,#d4afa9 50% 75%,#bd3b2d 75%)" decoding="async" data-tf-src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-670x299.jpg" alt="Prime Angling JDM Lures" width="670" height="299" class="tf_svg_lazy alignnone size-large wp-image-22243" data-tf-srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-670x299.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-300x134.jpg 300w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-190x85.jpg 190w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-768x343.jpg 768w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures.jpg 893w" data-tf-sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /><noscript><img decoding="async" data-tf-not-load src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-670x299.jpg" alt="Prime Angling JDM Lures" width="670" height="299" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-22243" srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-670x299.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-300x134.jpg 300w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-190x85.jpg 190w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures-768x343.jpg 768w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/prime-angling-jdm-lures.jpg 893w" sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /></noscript></a><br />
Matt and the team over at <a href="https://primeangling.co.uk/collections/jdm-lure-fishing/?sca_ref=3894212.AYJkJGQRZd&#038;sca_source=post-300525" target="_blank">Prime Angling</a> have been super busy finding all the latest and greatest lure fishing tackle over in Japan. It&#8217;s been a while since I did one of these so I thought I&#8217;d try and pull out some special items that grabbed my eye. Here goes: </p>
<div class="more-link-wrap"><a class="more-link" href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/2025/05/latest-jdm-tackle-at-prime-angling/">More</a></div></div></div></div></article> <article id="post-22167" class="post tf_clearfix cat-220 cat-7 post-22167 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-may category-notes tag-black-scorpion-fish tag-greece tag-hto-tempest-rock-rover tag-lesbos tag-travel has-post-title has-post-date has-post-category has-post-tag has-post-comment has-post-author "><div class="post-inner tf_clearfix"><span class="post-icon"></span><time datetime="2025-05-23" class="post-date entry-date updated">23rd May, 2025</time><h2 class="post-title entry-title"><a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/2025/05/light-lure-fishing-in-lesbos/">Light Lure Fishing in Lesbos</a></h2><div class="post-content"> <div class="entry-content"> <p><a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-scorpionfish-lesbos.jpg"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='670'%20height='894'%20viewBox=%270%200%20670%20894%27%3E%3C/svg%3E" loading="lazy" data-lazy="1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right,#eebb9e 25%,#7a9ad5 25% 50%,#7092cf 50% 75%,#6789c9 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#774232 25%,#674227 25% 50%,#0f0704 50% 75%,#a7c1e4 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#7f5851 25%,#865d3d 25% 50%,#28170f 50% 75%,#717246 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#275062 25%,#375b71 25% 50%,#658199 50% 75%,#6c869f 75%)" decoding="async" data-tf-src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-scorpionfish-lesbos-670x894.jpg" alt="Black Scorpionfish Lesbos" width="670" height="894" class="tf_svg_lazy alignnone size-large wp-image-22176" data-tf-srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-scorpionfish-lesbos-670x894.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-scorpionfish-lesbos-225x300.jpg 225w, https://light.rockfish