<br />
Managed to get some fishing in whilst on holiday on the Greek island of Lesbos. </p>
<div class="more-link-wrap"><a class="more-link" href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/2025/05/light-lure-fishing-in-lesbos/">More</a></div></div></div></div></article> <article id="post-20226" class="post tf_clearfix cat-5 cat-224 post-20226 type-post status-publish format-image has-post-thumbnail hentry category-image category-september tag-bream tag-dorset tag-scad tag-weymouth post_format-post-format-image has-post-title has-post-date has-post-category has-post-tag has-post-comment has-post-author "><div class="post-inner tf_clearfix"><span class="post-icon"></span><time datetime="2024-09-06" class="post-date entry-date updated">6th September, 2024</time><h2 class="post-title entry-title"><a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/2024/09/weymouth-september-bonanza/">Weymouth September Bonanza</a></h2><div class="post-content"> <div class="entry-content"> <p><a href="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/micro-scad-light-game.jpg"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='670'%20height='503'%20viewBox=%270%200%20670%20503%27%3E%3C/svg%3E" loading="lazy" data-lazy="1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right,#787169 25%,#61605c 25% 50%,#d9aea8 50% 75%,#425559 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#81786f 25%,#b07e73 25% 50%,#cacac8 50% 75%,#4b4d4c 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#d7ad9f 25%,#e6fffc 25% 50%,#673430 50% 75%,#8c9988 75%),linear-gradient(to right,#bb9b8e 25%,#d0aba2 25% 50%,#d9a99f 50% 75%,#715c3f 75%)" decoding="async" data-tf-src="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/micro-scad-light-game-670x503.jpg" alt="Micro Scad on Light Game" width="670" height="503" class="tf_svg_lazy alignnone size-large wp-image-20227" data-tf-srcset="https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/micro-scad-light-game-670x503.jpg 670w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/micro-scad-light-game-300x225.jpg 300w, https://light.rockfishing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2